beer.beer_description: Single hop American pale ale, dry hopped with Citra.

Hazy Pale ale beer style made with Latvian malted barley, oats, rye and 2 USA hops within boiling and dry hopping. Citrusy, lemon, lime, grapefruit aroma with medium body and sweet & bitter aftertaste.
